metadata.name: Palee, God of Monkey
metadata.description: Palee the Monkey King of Khiskrinda brother of Sugriva; The red rising sun monkey Palee is Emerald Green as he is the Son of Indra. Husband of Tara a beautiful divine nymph derived from Apsara underneath the ocean. Palee is known to be very courageous even if his wife begged him not to go to war he replied, “even if his son was the one who called for war he would still go to fight against him for the Gods.”
